WEBVTT

00:03:28.812 --> 00:03:31.552
Sada je kod kuće sa moje dvoje djece,

00:03:31.576 --> 00:03:34.266
a još jedno raste ovdje.

00:03:34.869 --> 00:03:40.044
(Pljesak)

00:03:40.594 --> 00:03:43.939
Kada radim, zovem ga svaka dva sata,

00:03:43.963 --> 00:03:47.753
a zna da, ukoliko mu se ne javim,

00:03:47.777 --> 00:03:49.204
treba nazvati moju vezu,

00:03:49.228 --> 00:03:52.390
onoga koji mi daje pristup priči,

00:03:52.414 --> 00:03:55.004
a kojemu vjerujem.

00:03:57.105 --> 00:03:59.130
Jednom sam u Gazi,

00:03:59.154 --> 00:04:04.093
tokom otmice britanskog novinara,
Alana Johnstona,